                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000402-63-defend527 t18000402-63-punish354"></join>
               Death
            </rs>. (Aged 25.)</p>
               <p>Colley, GUILTY Death. (Aged 20.)</p>
               <p>Barnett, GUILTY Death. (Aged 23.)</p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice GROSE.</p>
